                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Historic Photographs</Header>
                <Paragraph>From the earliest days of the TVA, photographers captured images of the agency's work and the cultural changes that followed. The TVA collection contains over 20,000 black-and-white negatives and over 5,000 original file prints. Its images span half a century, from 1933 to 1983.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
